data.description: Come see this amazing 5 bedroom/ 3.5 bathroom house in Walden ready for you to call HOME! This community has tons of Amenities like tennis and pickleball courts, gym, area swimming pool, lake conroe access, and close proximity to Margaritaville! This house has room to grow! 5 bedrooms plus gameroom, media room, and office! Fantastic split plan with primary bedroom down and all secondary bedrooms up.  2 story ceiling with wall of windows in the living room make this home light and bright! Features granite countertops, oversized two car garage with a 5' kick out for the motorcycle enthusiast,  an amazing covered balcony off the front secondary bedroom, great for guests! Freshly painted and ready for you to move in!!
